&lt;p&gt;Introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3554&quot; title=&quot;Hints are not replayed unless node was marked down&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3554&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3554&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  The problem is that until a compaction on hints occurs, tombstones are present causing the isEmpty() check to be false.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
